  "title": "Clinic Nurse (General Practitioner)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will play a key role in delivering high-quality patient care and supporting our clinical team at a busy GP practice.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead nurse-led clinics focused on wound care, immunisations, and chronic disease support to improve patient health outcomes</li><li>Assist clinical team by conducting health assessments and providing patient education to enhance patient understanding and self-care</li><li>Maintain accurate and comprehensive clinical records in compliance with best practice protocols to ensure quality and continuity of care</li><li>Collaborate effectively with healthcare professionals to support integrated patient management and clinical operations</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Registered Nurse with primary care or clinic experience</li><li>Demonstrate a warm, professional, and patient-focused approach to foster positive patient interactions</li><li>Exhibit strong teamwork and communication skills to contribute to a collaborative clinical environment</li></ul>",
